1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
On the field nearby,
the team “Zorza” Pęgów
plays its matches.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
The club has existed
for over 50 years.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Both children and adults
play football here.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,000
The field has been
full of sports life.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
The club also has
a very talented player.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Her name is
Alicja Pawlak.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
She played
37 times

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
for the Polish national team.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,000
With AZS Wrocław,
she became champion

10
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:40,000
of Poland 7 times.

11
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:44,000
She also won
the Polish Cup 3 times.

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,000
She played
in European competitions.

13
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:52,000
She scored 3 goals,
even as a defender.

14
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
One was special —
directly from a corner.

15
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
It was against AEK.

16
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:06,000
Do you want
to follow her path?

17
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:13,000
The club and training
are waiting for you!